        <section class="py-16 bg-white border-b border-gray-100">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-10">
                    <div class="reveal w-full lg:w-1/2">
                        <h2 class="font-heading text-brand-green font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-xs sm:text-sm mb-2">Expert Advice</h2>
                        <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-dark mb-4">Empowering Homeowners with Facts</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
                            Investing in your roofline is an important decision. At Lancashire Aluminium Seamless Guttering, we believe in complete transparency. We've compiled the most common questions our customers ask to help you make an informed choice.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
                            If you have a specific query regarding your property or need details about our Cut & Drop service, please do not hesitate to contact our friendly local team directly.
                        </p>
